  "translations": {
    "en": "Then be mindful of your wudu, for it is a condition for the fulfilment of prayers. Wash your mouth three times, draw water in your nose three times, then wash your face, then the right hand, then the left hand, then wipe your head and two feet. Surely, I saw the Prophet, peace be upon him and his progeny, do the same. And know that wudu is half of faith.",
    "ur": "Then be mindful of your wudu, for it is a condition for the fulfilment of prayers. Wash your mouth three times, draw water in your nose three times, then wash your face, then the right hand, then the left hand, then wipe your head and two feet. Surely, I saw the Prophet, peace be upon him and his progeny, do the same. And know that wudu is half of faith.",
